ABAPHATHI beMaritzburg United bamise zonke izinhlelo ngemuva kokusabalala kwezwi ebelibika ngokudlula emhlabeni komdlali wayo obethembisa, uLuyanda Ntshangase. UNtshangase (21), udlule emhlabeni ngoLwesihlany ngemuva kokulaliswa eRoyal Hospital, eMgungundlovu izinyanga ezimbili ngemuva kokushaywa wumphezulu lapho kuzilolongela khona iqembu, ngaphandle kwaseHarry Gwala Stadium. UNtshangase ukhulele kwiZichwe engaphansi kukaThabo Dladla ungowaseMbali, e-1, eMgungundlovu. Ubenza unyaka wesithathu kwiSocial Science e-University of KwaZulu-Natal eMgungundlovu. UFarook Kadodia usihlalo weThe Team of Choice nobezwakala ukuthi wephukile emoyeni, utshele Isolezwe ngoMgqibelo ngokumiswa kwazo zonke izinhlelo zeqembu ngemuva kokuzwa lezi zindaba. “Lesi yisikhathi esingesihle kithina njengoba sizilele ukudlula emhlabeni kukaLuyanda. Sithathe isinqumo sokumisa okwesikhashana kuleli sonto zonke izinhlelo zebhola. “Siyoze siqale ukukhuluma ngebhola nangemidlalo yethu ngesonto elizayo. “Njengamanje sifisa ukududuza umndeni wakwaNtshangase ngokushiywa yilungu lomndeni. “Lesi sehlo senzeke ngesikhathi esibi lapho 
iqembu libhekene nemidlalo emqoka. Izindaba ezibuhlungu. Sihlalele ethembeni lokuthi ngeke zibe nomthelela omubi enkundleni. “Nakanjani sizobaphazamisa abadlali ngoba bebesondelene naye,” kubeka uKadodia. UNtshangase 
