ijezi ngenxa yokuthi 
kwasuke kwaqhamuka abanye abafana abancane abavutha uphondo. UNtshangase ungumdlali wesithathu weMaritzburg eminyakeni emithathu ukudlula emhlabeni ngengozi. Ngaphambi kwakhe kwashona uMondli Cele ngo 2016, kwathi ngokuqala kwesizini kwaphinde kwadlula emhlabeni uMlondi Dlamini. Bobabili laba badlali badlule ngengozi yemoto njengoba yena eleleswe wumphezulu. 
I-United isesikhathini esimqoka sesizini lapho isethubeni lokuqeda endaweni yesithathu iphinde ikhale yemuke nesicoco seNedbank Cup. Emdlalweni wamanqamu kwiNedbank Cup izoshukana neFree State Stars eCape Town Stadium ngoMeyi 19. Ukunqoba kwayo izohlabana ngo-7.30 
million bese izibekisela indawo kwiCaf Confederation Cup. NgoMgqibelo izotholana phezulu neLamontville Golden Arrows emdlalweni wabakhaya wokuvala iligi, eHarry Gwala Stadium ngo 3 ntambama. Leli qembu libheke ukuqeda endaweni yesithathu. Njengamanje lihlezi endaweni yesine.